{"id": "1dcf2d6f978d", "timestamp": "2026-04-09T15:36:21.316450", "error_type": "Bot/Agent Runtime Error", "error_message": "Automatic session resume failed, so sending the status directly. Agent was aborted. Queue has 2 entries that shouldn't be there \u2014 cleared before restarting. Old entries from a previous session.", "severity": "critical", "file_location": "N/A", "language": "Bot framework (unspecified)", "context_summary": "A Telegram bot conversation showing a bot agent that failed to resume its session automatically, was aborted, had stale queue entries from a previous session, and the developer is frustrated about unauthorized use of the Blackbox API within research loops.", "fix": "**Cause:** The agent's session state was persisted to a queue but never atomically cleared on shutdown, so stale entries from the previous run blocked the new session from initializing cleanly and triggered an abort.\n\n**Fix:** On every agent startup (before resuming or creating a session), explicitly flush/purge the queue first:\n\n```python\nagent.queue.clear()  # or redis: r.delete(\"agent:queue:<session_id>\")\nsession = agent.resume_or_create_session()\n```", "screenshot_b64": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAA8AAAAIcCAIAAAC2P1AsAAEAAElEQVR42uyddZhdRdLGq7r7yPXxSTJx9xACQYK7O7u4LeyysLDY4v7hu8DiDou7uwUICSEQICHuMslkfOb6se76/rgTDxCSIQToH/d5mNx7tI+9p7r6Lew9bEfQaDQajUaj0Wg06wfTTaDRaDQajUaj", "notified": true}
{"id": "1dcf2d6f978d", "timestamp": "2026-04-09T15:36:28.919771", "error_type": "Bot/Agent Runtime Error", "error_message": "Automatic session resume failed, so sending the status directly. Agent was aborted. Queue has 2 entries that shouldn't be there \u2014 I cleared it before restarting. Old entries from a previous session.", "severity": "critical", "file_location": "N/A", "language": "N/A (Telegram bot/agent framework)", "context_summary": "A developer is communicating with a bot called 'hedgeclaw' via Telegram. The bot reported automatic session resume failure, agent abortion, and stale queue entries from a previous session. The developer appears frustrated, telling the bot to stop using Blackbox API and expressing anger at unexpected behavior. The Bot Shoppe chat also shows 'Error Detected' notification, suggesting multiple bot errors are occurring simultaneously.", "fix": "**Cause:** The bot's message queue is persisting stale entries across restarts because the session state is not being cleared/flushed before reinitializing, causing the resumed session to replay old queued messages from the previous run.\n\n**Fix:** Add an explicit queue flush and session invalidation at startup, before the agent initializes \u2014 e.g., `await bot.deleteWebhook({ drop_pending_updates: true })` (for Telegram's `telegraf`/`node-telegram-bot-api`) to drop all pending updates, and clear a", "screenshot_b64": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAA8AAAAIcCAIAAAC2P1AsAAEAAElEQVR42uyddZhdRdLGq7r7yPXxSTJx9xACQYK7O7u4LeyysLDY4v7hu8DiDou7uwUICSEQICHuMslkfOb6se76/rgTDxCSIQToH/d5mNx7tI+9p7r6Lew9bEfQaDQajUaj0Wg06wfTTaDRaDQajUaj", "notified": true}
{"id": "1dcf2d6f978d", "timestamp": "2026-04-09T15:36:36.788131", "error_type": "Bot/Agent Runtime Error", "error_message": "Automatic session resume failed, so sending the status directly. Agent was aborted. Queue has 2 entries that shouldn't be there \u2014 cleared before restarting. Old entries from a previous session detected.", "severity": "critical", "file_location": "N/A", "language": "N/A (Telegram bot chat log)", "context_summary": "A Telegram bot named 'hedgeclaw' experienced a session failure \u2014 automatic session resume failed, the agent was aborted, and stale queue entries from a previous session were found. The user is frustrated and demanding the Blackbox AI API be disabled, suggesting the bot is misbehaving in research loops.", "fix": "**Cause:** The bot's session state wasn't properly cleared on crash/restart, causing the agent to attempt resuming a stale queue with 2 orphaned entries from the previous session, triggering the abort.\n\n**Fix:** Add explicit session cleanup on startup before the agent initializes:\n\n```python\n# At bot startup, before agent.run() or session.start()\nawait session.clear()          # flush stale queue entries\nawait agent.reset_state()      # reset agent FSM to idle\nsession_store.delete(bot_id)   # pu", "screenshot_b64": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAA8AAAAIcCAIAAAC2P1AsAAEAAElEQVR42uyddZhdRdLGq7r7yPXxSTJx9xACQYK7O7u4LeyysLDY4v7hu8DiDou7uwUICSEQICHuMslkfOb6se76/rgTDxCSIQToH/d5mNx7tI+9p7r6Lew9bEfQaDQajUaj0Wg06wfTTaDRaDQajUaj", "notified": false}
